{"tid":1887156,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"NBA新秀挑戰賽出現「武漢加油」 強國球迷不領情：「不道歉就抵制到底」","createTime":"2020-02-19T10:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T12:09:23.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"70f4f0b0adbd8d61bdd2949885db966a7d611b70","tid":1887156,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"〔體育中心／綜合報導〕去年火箭隊總經理莫雷「挺自由、撐香港」的言論，引發中國人不滿，大規模抵制，而NBA官方當時也拒絕道歉，但卻因此損失大把鈔票，如今官方積極向中國示好。<br />\n<br />\n今年的新秀挑戰賽，公牛聯合中心球場大螢幕上出現「武漢加油（&ldquo;Stay Strong Wuhan&rdquo;）」的口號。同時近期NBA積極幫助中國對抗武漢肺炎，先後捐出價值超過1850萬人民幣的醫療設備到中國。<br />\n<br />\n但中國大部分的網友態度一致，「我們感謝NBA捐助，但一碼歸一碼，莫雷的惡劣行為，NBA官方應該公開道歉，若不願意道歉，還是必須繼續抵制，且抵制到底。」<br />\n<br />\n席爾瓦在明星週的記者會上談到了那則推特引發的後續效應，以及聯盟損失的金錢：「關於確切的損失金額，還有一小部分是不確定的。我認為損失的金額將會達到上億美元。」<br />\n<br />\n根據美媒報導，NBA本季收視率嚴重下滑，三大全美直播平台ESPN、TNT及ABC收視率比同期下滑12%，而ABC最慘，慘跌16%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3070280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3070280&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=92074d35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3070280&h=8ec5345d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3070280</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAh3pwc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAh3pwc.jpg&h=81b104c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d72d535326b9faf46d43e513e79b527c0629734a","tid":1887156,"uid":50719,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ed62b0756b29eafd329fbf9e3b9d8a00af5e3e","tid":1887156,"uid":286309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"中國人睇CBA啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae216e0aa930d6d9b1139451260a31d4ec13accb"